<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Verify Your Email for Quizzie</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Quizzie!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for registering. To activate your account and start creating/taking quizzes, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </p>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p><a href="{{verificationLink}}">{{verificationLink}}</a></p>
        <p>This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
        <p>If you did not register for Quizzie, please ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Quizzie Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>